      "updated": 1773957648777,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Security rules set at OneLake level are inherited by all Fabric engines\n\nDefine custom roles w/permission sets\n* Restrict access by schema, table, column, or row\n    * Read/ReadWrite access\n    * SQL statements to filter rows\nUsers/groups assigned to roles using Entra ID\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Security rules set at OneLake level are inherited by all Fabric engines\n\nDefine custom roles w/permission sets\n* Restrict access by schema, table, column, or row\n    * Read/ReadWrite access\n    * SQL statements to filter rows\nUsers/groups assigned to roles using Entra ID\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
